WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:07.360
THIS WEEK AT INTERIOR…

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:12.129
SENIOR FEDERAL OFFICIALS AND COMMUNITY LEADERS
COMING TOGETHER IN WASHINGTON DC THIS WEEK

00:00:12.129 --> 00:00:15.550
FOR THE ANNUAL ASIAN AMERICANS AND PACIFIC
ISLANDERS SUMMIT…

00:00:15.550 --> 00:00:18.500
SECRETARY JEWELL WAS AMONG THOSE ATTENDING,
AND TAKING PART IN A

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:22.960
CABINET PANEL DISCUSSION ON PROGRESS IN THE
COMMUNITY DURING THE OBAMA ADMINISTRATION.

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:26.150
MAY IS ASIAN AMERICAN AND PACIFIC ISLANDER
HERITAGE MONTH…

00:00:26.150 --> 00:00:30.180
THIS YEAR’S SUMMIT BROUGHT OUT MORE THAN
2000 COMMUNITY MEMBERS, TO TALK ABOUT A RANGE

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:34.620
OF ISSUES, EVERYTHING FROM ECONOMIC GROWTH
AND EDUCATION TO HEALTHCARE, CIVIL RIGHTS

00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:38.649
AND IMMIGRATION.

00:00:38.649 --> 00:00:44.680
(MUSIC PLAYS “TAPS”)

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:49.160
A SOLEMN CEREMONY THIS WEEK TO HONOR THOSE
WHO HAVE FALLEN IN THE LINE OF DUTY, SERVING

00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:51.270
AND PROTECTING THEIR FELLOW CITIZENS.

00:00:51.270 --> 00:00:56.629
SECRETARY JEWELL SPEAKING AT THE LAW ENFORCEMENT
OFFICER MEMORIAL CEREMONY AT D-A-R CONSTITUTION

00:00:56.629 --> 00:00:59.559
HALL, PART OF THE CELEBRATION OF NATIONAL
POLICE WEEK.

00:00:59.559 --> 00:01:05.880
IT IS A TIME TO REMEMBER THIS SOBERING STATISTIC
– THAT, ON AVERAGE, A POLICE

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:13.650
OFFICER IS KILLED EVERY TWO DAYS WHILE DOING
HIS OR HER JOB IN SERVICE TO OUR NATION.

00:01:13.650 --> 00:01:17.799
LAST YEAR, 126 OFFICERS WERE LOST NATIONWIDE.

00:01:17.799 --> 00:01:24.610
WE’VE ETCHED THEIR NAMES INTO THE STONE
WALLS OF THE NATIONAL LAW ENFORCEMENT MEMORIAL

00:01:24.610 --> 00:01:27.860
SO THAT WE’LL NEVER FORGET THEIR STORIES.

00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:34.021
THE USGS CONTINUES TO MONITOR EARTHQUAKE ACTIVITY
IN NEPAL, WHERE A MAGNITUDE 7.3 AFTERSHOCK

00:01:34.021 --> 00:01:39.470
STRUCK THIS WEEK, FOLLOWING THE 7.8 EARTHQUAKE
NEAR KATHMANDU ON APRIL 25TH…

00:01:39.470 --> 00:01:44.250
SCIENTISTS SAY MORE THAN 100 AFTERSHOCKS HAVE
OCCURRED AND ARE LIKELY TO CONTINUE, BUT WILL

00:01:44.250 --> 00:01:46.909
HAPPEN LESS OFTEN AS TIME GOES BY.

00:01:46.909 --> 00:01:51.850
SECRETARY JEWELL JOINED DOZENS OF KIDS, PARENTS,
TEACHERS AND ONLINE INNOVATORS THIS WEEK FOR

00:01:51.850 --> 00:01:55.549
A WHITE HOUSE SPONSORED EVENT AIMED AT RE-CONNECTING
YOUTH TO THE GREAT OUTDOORS…

00:01:55.549 --> 00:01:58.540
IT’S ALL PART OF THE *EVERY KID IN A PARK*
INITIATIVE…

00:01:58.540 --> 00:02:03.520
THIS EVENT WAS PART OF THE WEBSITE DESIGN
PROCESS TO CREATE LOW TECH PROTOTYPES OF ONLINE

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:07.160
GAMES AND ACTIVITIES THAT APPEAL TO THE NATION’S
YOUNG PEOPLE.

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:11.950
THE NATIONAL PARK SERVICE AND YMCA OF THE
USA *ALSO* JOINED FORCES THIS WEEK TO GET

00:02:11.950 --> 00:02:13.280
EVERY KID IN A PARK…

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:17.550
THEY LAUNCHED THE *PLAY, LEARN, SERVE, AND
WORK SUMMER CAMP PROGRAM*, PART OF INTERIOR’S

00:02:17.550 --> 00:02:23.000
50 CITIES INITIATIVE TO INCREASE AWARENESS,
SUPPORT AND PARTICIPATION IN OUTDOOR PROGRAMS.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.800
FIND OUT MORE AT NPS.GOV

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:28.940
AND THE NATIONAL WILDLIFE REFUGE SYSTEM HAS
A NEW CHIEF…

00:02:28.940 --> 00:02:33.650
CYNTHIA MARTINEZ IS A 21-YEAR VETERAN OF THE
FISH AND WILDLIFE SERVICE, NOW SELECTED TO

00:02:33.650 --> 00:02:38.480
LEAD THE WORLD’S PREMIER SYSTEM OF PUBLIC
LANDS AND WATERS SET ASIDE TO CONSERVE FISH,

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:39.480
WILDLIFE AND PLANTS…

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:43.489
THERE’S A NATIONAL WILDLIFE REFUGE IN EVERY
U-S STATE AND TERRITORY.

00:02:43.489 --> 00:02:45.390
THAT’S THIS WEEK, AT INTERIOR.

